sections.heading: of statutes; not correlated; not reconcilable; Revisor of Statutes; duties
sections.text: When one section of the statutes is amended in two or more bills in the same session of the Legislature and has not been correlated as a part of the normal legislative process and the amendments are not entirely reconcilable
